description:
This order is made to order, please allow 1-2 week(s) after receiving your final artwork on label to finish your order.

{ QUANTITY }

50 - 2 oz. travel tin soy candles. Please send me an email at usap@purepalette.com if you would like more than 50. Price of 2 oz. travel tin when you place an order more than 50 and less than 74 tins, it will be at $3.00 per tin.

{ SCENT (CERTIFIED ESSENTIAL OILS) }

Please select your scent choice by selecting your choice from a drop-down menu. You have up to 2 scent choices. You can add additional choice by adding your scent name on your note at check out.

{ YOUR CUSTOM ARTWORK }

I can accept your artwork in .pdf or Illustrator file only. Sorry I can not accept artwork in .jpg file.

{ DIMENSION & BURN TIME}

+ 2 Oz. Soy Candle
+ 2" Diameter x 1.50" Height
+ 5 Hours plus

{ INGREDIENTS }

:> Soy Wax
:> Certified Essential Oils
:> Cotton Wick

Full 2 oz. soybean candle is carefully crafted with premium grade soy wax , 20% more scented oil to create strong scent throw. Cotton wick is used for clean burning in your home environment. White color and NO color dye is added

{ CARE }

+ Trim wick to 1/8" to ensure even burning & prevent soot and flame from becoming too large.
+ Recommend to read Care & Caution note on the bottom of the container prior to using the soy candle.

{ PACKAGE }

It comes in travel tin with lid.

{ SCENT (FRAGRANCE OIL) }

Phthalate free fragrance oil is added and crafted to create a wonderful scent in your home. 

{ DIMENSION & BURN TIME}

+ 2.5" Diameter x 1.75" Height
+ 15 Hours plus

{ INGREDIENTS }

:> Soy Wax
:> Phthalate free fragrance Oil
:> Cotton Wick

Full 4 oz. soybean candle is carefully crafted with pure 100% soy wax , 20% more scented oil to create strong scent throw. Cotton wick is used for clean burning in your home environment. White color and NO color dye is added

{ CARE }

+ Trim wick to 1/8" to ensure even burning & prevent soot and flame from becoming too large.
+ Recommend to read Care & Caution note on the bottom of the container prior to using the soy candle.

{ PACKAGE }

It comes in travel tin with lid.

SCENT (PURE NATURAL ESSENTIAL OIL BLEND) }

Citrus Lavender scent is one of my favorite custom blended scent. Citrus Lavender blended scent helps energizing your mood and uplifting your spirit.

{ INGREDIENTS }

Full 10.5 oz. botanical bath salts in glass jar is carefully formulated with dead sea salt, Himalayan pink salt, lavender bud, sodium bicarbonate, vitamin E and sweet almond oil

{ Benefits }

Bathing with dead sea salt and Himalayan bath salts will helps heal dry, scaling, irritated skin. Salt water bathing reduces inflammation of the muscles and joints, relaxes muscles and relieves pain and soreness. Calcium which is one mineral ingredient in dead sea salt will helps stimulating circulation, hydrates the skin, increases moisture retention, promotes cellular regeneration and detoxifies the skin.
